OL,6,FFrom tomorrow morning (Monday, 9th
OL,7,FSeptember) passengers who board trains
OL,8,Fwithout a ticket face being fined on
OL,9,Fmore lines.
OL,11,FThe penalty fare zone between Severn
OL,12,FTunnel Junction and Carmarthen is
OL,13,Fbeing extended to most of south Wales,
OL,14,Fincluding the Treherbert, Aberdare,
OL,15,FMerthyr, Coryton, Penarth, Rhymney,
OL,16,FBarry, Bridgend and the Ebbw Vale
OL,17,Flines.
OL,19,FFare dodgers face a fine of double the
OL,20,Fticket fare or #20, whichever is
OL,21,Fgreater.
